%20place.%20Suddenly%20the%20phone%20connection%20got%20disrupted%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20woman's%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLater%2C%20I%20got%20to%20know%20that%20there%20has%20been%20an%20explosion%20at%20the%20place%20where%20Sheeja%20was%20staying.%20I%20called%20up%20her%20friends%20to%20enquire%20about%20Sheeja%2C%20as%20I%20was%20told%20that%20they%20can't%20step%20out%20or%20go%20anywhere%2C%20due%20to%20restrictions.%20After%20a%20gap%20of%203-4%20hours%2C%20I%20was%20told%20by%20her%20friends%20that%20she%20has%20minor%20injury%20on%20her%20hands%20and%20she%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20medical%20caregiver%20will%20have%20to%20undergo%20spine%20injury%2C%20said%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReeling%20from%20Hamas'%20unprecedented%20ground%2C%20air%20and%20sea%20attacks%2C%20Israel%20has%20counted%20over%20700%20dead%20and%20launched%20a%20withering%20barrage%20of%20strikes%20on%20Gaza%20that%20have%20killed%20560%20people%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20told%20that%20there%20are%20injuries%20on%20her%20leg%2C%20chest%2C%20stomach.%20After%20she%20was%20operated%20I%20got%20a%20video%20call%20from%20her%20through%20her%20friends%2C%20that's%20when%20I%20got%20to%20see%20Sheeja.%20During%20the%20conversation%2C%20I%20was%20told%20that%20she%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20another%20hospital%20for%20surgery%20on%20spine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20foreigners%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20violence%2C%20including%20victims%20from%20Thailand%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20France%2C%20Britain%2C%20US%2C%20Canada%20and%20Cambodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20received%20any%20call%20from%20embassy%20or%20from%20our%20government.%20What%20I%20have%20to%20say%20is%20that%20the%20government%20of%20India%20should%20intervene%20and%20help%20us%20out%20in%20this%20need%20of%20hour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Anand's%20brother-in-law%2C%20Devan%2C%20has%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20she%20has%20been%20working%20as%20a%20caregiver%20in%20Israel%20for%20the%20past%20seven%20years%20and%20that%20she%20had%20come%20to%20Kerala%20last%20year%20for%20a%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20informed%20that%20she%20has%20been%20transferred%20to%20another%20hospital%20for%20spine%20injury.%20We%20were%20told%20that%20she%20has%20got%20injury%20on%20her%20hands%20and%20legs.%20On%20Saturday%20at%2012.30%20noon%20she%20was%20on%20a%20video%20call%20with%20her%20husband.%20Her%20friends%20told%20us%20that%20she%20is%20injured%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sjiji%2C%20sister%20of%20Ms%20Anand.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20gun%20battles%20are%20raging%20in%20towns%20and%20on%20highways%2C%20nearly%2018%2C000%20citizens%20are%20stuck%20in%20Israel.%20The%20majority%20of%20them%20are%20caregivers%2C%20IT%20professionals%20and%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20embassy%20at%20Jerusalem%20and%20the%20Representative%20Office%20of%20India%20in%20Palestine%20on%20Saturday%20issued%20advisories%20asking%20Indian%20nationals%20in%20respective%20countries%20to%20%26quot%3Bremain%20vigilant%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdirectly%20contact%20the%20Office%26quot%3B%20in%20case%20of%20emergency%20as%20a%20full-fledged%20war%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20ruling%20Hamas%20group%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696871400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fvjgb61os_kerala-woman-israel-1200-_625x300_09_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-woman-injured-in-missile-attack-by-hamas-in-israel-4465696%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian%20woman%20in%20Israel%20was%20injured%20in%20the%20massive%20surprise%20attack%20on%20the%20country%20with%20a%20barrage%20of%20rockets%20by%20Hamas%20while%20she%2