w%2F104292781.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fheavy-flooding-in-southern-myanmar-displaces-over-14000-people%2Famp_articleshow%2F104292781.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cricket%20proposed%20for%20inclusion%20in%202028%20LA%20Olympics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696870253000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104292658%2Cimgsize-13666.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fla28s-recommendation-for-inclusion-of-cricket-in-olympics-delights-icc%2Farticleshow%2F104292674.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Following%20a%20comprehensive%20two-year%20process%2C%20during%20which%20the%20ICC%20collaborated%20closely%20with%20LA28%2C%20the%20selection%20of%20sports%20to%20be%20added%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20now%20incorporates%20cricket.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fla28s-recommendation-for-inclusion-of-cricket-in-olympics-delights-icc%2Farticleshow%2F104292674.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMalicious%20Campaign%20To%20Tarnish%20Image%26quot%3B%3A%20Adani%20Group%20Slams%20Financial%20Times%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20today%20slammed%20the%20UK-based%20newspaper%20Financial%20Times'%20for%20%26quot%3Braking%20up%20an%20old%2C%20baseless%20allegation%20of%20over-invoicing%20of%20coal%20imports%26quot%3B.%20The%20group%20accused%20it%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bmalicious%20campaign%20to%20drag%20down%20its%20market%20value%20and%20tarnish%20its%20reputation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bhaving%20failed%20earlier%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Financial%20Times%20is%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20another%20effort%20to%20financially%20destabilise%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BContinuing%20their%20relentless%20campaign%2C%20the%20next%20attack%20is%20being%20fronted%20by%20Dan%20McCrum%20of%20the%20Financial%20Times%2C%20who%20jointly%20with%20the%20OCCRP%20put%20out%20a%20false%20narrative%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group%20on%2031%20August%202023.%20The%20OCCRP%20is%20funded%20by%20George%20Soros%2C%20who%20has%20openly%20declared%20his%20hostility%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20group%20also%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20mere%20coincidence%20that%20such%20stories%20have%20an%20uncanny%20ability%20to%20appear%20just%20before%20the%20hearing%20dates%20of%20important%20cases%20in%20India's%20courts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%2C%20while%20denying%20all%20such%20allegations%20as%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20and%20baseless%26quot%3B%2C%20condemned%20such%20%26quot%3Bdeliberate%2C%20and%20motivated%20attempts%20to%20destabilise%26quot%3B%20it.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20a%20law-abiding%20company%20which%20is%20fully%20compliant%20with%20all%20rules%2C%20regulations%20and%20disclosure%20requirements%20with%20full%20respect%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20part%20of%20their%20extended%20campaign%20to%20advance%20vested%20interests%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20public%20interest%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20proposed%20story%20by%20the%20publication%20is%20based%20on%20the%20DRI's%20General%20Alert%20Circular%20dated%20March%2030%2C%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20publication%20has%20%26quot%3Bsingled%20out%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20while%20the%20DRI's%20circular%20mentions%20as%20many%20as%2040%20importers%20including%20the%20Adani%20Group%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Customs%2C%20Excise%20and%20Services%20Tax%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20(CESTAT)%20had%20however%20quashed%20the%20case.%20DRI%20went%20in%20for%20an%20appeal%20but%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20this%20year%20dismissed%20its%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20said%20the%20DRI's%20show%20cause%20notice%20alleging%20over-valuation%20in%20the%20import%20of%20coal%20was%20dismissed%20by%20the%20appellate%20tribunal%20(CESTAT).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20FT's%20proposed%20storyline%20is%20a%20clever%20recycling%20and%20selective%20misrepresentation%20of%20publicly%20available%20facts%20and%20information%20with%20a%20deliberate%20and%20mischievous%20suppression%20of%20judicial%20decisions%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20predetermined%20conclusion.%20It%20shows%20scant%20respect%20for%20India's%20regulatory%20and%20judicial%20processes%20and%20authorities.%20It%20also%20deliberately%20ignores%20the%20fact%20that%20coal%20procurement%20in%20India%20on%20a%20long-term%20supply%20basis%20is%20done%20through%20an%20open%2C%20transparent%2C%20global%20bidding%20process%20thereby%20eliminating%20any%20possibility%20of%20price%20manipulation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETariff%20fixation%20by%20the%20Central%20Electricity%20Regulatory%20Commission%20(CERC)%20is%20an%20open%2C%20transparent%2C%20independent%20process%20where%20the%20tariffs%20are%20fixed%20after%20carefully%20evaluating%20all%20variables%20and%20in%20consultations%20with%20the%20power%20generator%2C%20distributor%20and%20retail%20consumers%2C%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20multiple%20stakeholders%20have%20multiple%20opportunities%20to%20look%20at%20all%20aspects%20determining%20the%20tariffs%2C%20including%20the%20import%20value%20of%20coal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHence%20the%20question%20of%20over-invoicing%20or%20price%20manipulation%20does%20not%20arise%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22pub