008%20till%20September%202023%2C%206%2C407%20Palestinians%20were%20recorded%20to%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20more%20than%20half%20through%20missile%20attacks.%20During%20the%20same%20period%2C%20the%20UN%20recorded%20the%20death%20of%20308%20Israelis%20in%20conflict%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%20onslaught%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20the%20last%20major%20fight%20had%20been%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-palestine-sheikh-jarrah-al-aqsa-jerusalem%5C%22%3EMay%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Israelis%20put%20up%20metal%20barriers%20near%20the%20Damascus%20gate%20of%20Jerusalem%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20the%20Al-Aqsa%20mosque%2C%20during%20the%20month%20of%20Ramzan.%20The%2011%20days%20of%20fighting%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20349%20Palestinians%20and%2011%20Israelis.%20One%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcentre-confirms-death-of-kerala-woman-in-a-rocket-attack-on-israel%2Farticle60683858.ece%5C%22%3EIndian%20caregiver%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20lost%20her%20life%20in%20a%20rocket%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatistics.btselem.org%2Fen%2Fall-fatalities%2Fby-date-of-incident%3Fsection%3Doverall%26tab%3Doverview%5C%22%3EB%E2%80%99Tselem%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20Israeli%20human-rights%20organisation%2C%201%2C0712%20Palestinians%20and%201%2C330%20Israelis%20had%20been%20killed%20since%202000%20till%20this%20year%2C%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20current%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20Intifada%20in%201987%20led%20to%20major%20bloodshed%20in%20Palestine%2C%20which%20eventually%20led%20to%20the%20Oslo%20peace%20accords.%20However%2C%20%C2%A0the%20violence%20did%20not%20let%20up%20with%20suicide%20bombings%20taking%20place%20inside%20Israel%20and%20Gaza%20continued%20to%20be%20further%20constricted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20intifada%20began%20a%20few%20months%20after%20the%20failed%20Camp%20David%20talks.%20Israel%20withdrew%20from%20Gaza%20in%202005%2C%20but%20there%20were%20even%20more%20restrictions%20on%20the%20movement%20of%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20major%20spike%20in%20casualties%20in%202008%20and%202009%20when%20Israel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.middleeastmonitor.com%2F20181227-remembering-israels-2008-war-on-gaza%2F%5C%22%3Elaunched%20an%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20rockets%20were%20launched%20towards%20the%20Israeli%20town%20of%20Sderot.%20In%20total%2C%20around%201%2C400%20Palestinians%20and%2013%20Israelis%20were%20killed%2C%20before%20a%20ceasefire%20was%20announced%20in%20January%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20deadliest%20year%20for%20Palestinian%20casualties%20had%20been%202014%20when%20Hamas%20kidnapped%20and%20killed%20three%20Israeli%20teenagers.%20The%20seven%20weeks%20of%20war%2C%20which%20included%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20and%20Hamas%20rocket%20launches%20left%20over%202%2C310%20Palestinians%20dead.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ynet.co.il%2Fhome%2F0%2C7340%2CL-11584%2C00.html%5C%22%3Efatalities%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Israeli%20side%20were%2073%2C%20which%20included%2067%20soldiers%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696869384000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09220317%2FFlickr_-_Israel_Defense_Forces_-_Israel_Under_Fire_from_Rocket_Attacks_1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchart-6407-palestinians-and-308-israelis-killed-in-violence-in-last-15-years%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22So%20far%2C%20there%20have%20been%20over%201%2C200%20fatalities%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20border%20following%20the%20latest%20bout%20of%20violence%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchart-6407-palestinians-and-308-israelis-killed-in-violence-in-last-15-years%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%