y%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani'%20co-starring%20Ranveer%20Singh%2C%20Jaya%20Bachchan%2C%20Shabana%20Azmi%20and%20Dharmendra%2C%20directed%20by%20Karan%20Johar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fheres-what-alia-bhatt-has-to-say-on-the-success-of-rocky-aur-rani-kii-prem-kahaani-with-ranveer-singh%2Farticleshow%2F104291088.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22''Could%20Have%20Broken%20A%20Tooth''%3A%20Man%20Finds%20Screw%20In%20A%20Bag%20of%20Chips%20At%20KFC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20in%20the%20UK%20was%20left%20shocked%20after%20he%20found%20a%20metal%20screw%20in%20a%20meal%20from%20KFC.%20The%20incident%20happened%20last%20week%20when%20Callum%20Feehan%2C%2025%2C%20bought%20a%20meal%20from%20KFC's%20outlet%20in%20Canterbury%20Street%2C%20Gillingham%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2023%2F10%2F09%2Fman-finds-screw-in-kfc-chips-19630080%2F%3Fico%3Dmosaic_home%5C%22%3EMetro%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%20After%20coming%20home%2C%20he%20put%20a%20handful%20of%20chips%20in%20his%20mouth%20and%20felt%20something%20metal%2C%20and%20found%20a%20fried%20screw.%20He%20said%20he%20''could%20have%20broken%20a%20tooth''%20if%20he%20had%20bitten%20into%20the%20screw.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20''I%20bought%20the%20meal%20and%20came%20home.%20I'd%20literally%20put%20a%20handful%20of%20chips%20in%20my%20mouth%20and%20I%20could%20feel%20something%20rattling%20around%20in%20my%20mouth%2C%20and%20when%20I%20pulled%20it%20out%20it%20was%20a%20fried%20screw.%20I%20could%20have%20broken%20a%20tooth%20%E2%80%93%20thankfully%20I%20didn't.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IT%20worker%20contacted%20KFC%20on%20X%20but%20said%20they%20only%20replied%20when%20he%20threatened%20to%20inform%20Environmental%20Health.%C2%A0He%20added%20that%20they%20haven't%20replied%20since%20he%20sent%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20metal%20object.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20overly%20happy.%20I%20immediately%20contacted%20KFC%20on%20Twitter%2C%20or%20X%20now%2C%20and%20they%20completely%20ignored%20me%20for%20at%20least%2048%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20when%20I%20threatened%20them%20with%20Environmental%20Health%20that%20they%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98They%20asked%20for%20a%20photo%20and%20asked%20where%20it%20was%20purchased%20and%20said%20they'd%20get%20back%20to%20me.%20That%20was%20Sunday%2C%20but%20there's%20been%20nothing%20since%2C''%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20customer%20was%20also%20upset%20at%20the%20lack%20of%20response%20and%20accountability%20from%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''I%20go%20down%20to%20that%20KFC%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20week.%20I've%20had%20a%20few%20issues%20before%20but%20nothing%20major.%20It's%20more%20concerning%20that%20they%20don't%20seem%20to%20be%20concerned%20that%20I%20found%20it%20in%20my%20food.%C2%A0They're%20not%20really%20taking%20what%20I%20told%20them%20seriously%2C%20which%20is%20what%20I'd%20expect%20from%20somewhere%20I%20go%20quite%20regularly.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20KFC%20spokesman%20later%20said%3A%20%E2%80%98We%20have%20strict%20processes%20in%20place%20to%20prevent%20any%20foreign%20objects%20from%20entering%20the%20food%20we%20serve.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20take%20claims%20of%20this%20nature%20extremely%20seriously%20and%20can%20confirm%20our%20team%20is%20investigating%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20urgency.%20We%20are%20also%20in%20touch%20with%20Callum%20to%20keep%20him%20updated.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20back%2C%C2%A0a%20person%C2%A0found%20a%20spider%20inside%20his%20KFC%20chicken%20wrap%20at%20an%20outlet%20in%20Newport%2C%20South%20Wales.%20The%20man%2C%20named%20Luke%20Hatherall%2C%20discovered%20the%20dead%20arthropod%20on%20the%20lettuce%2C%20after%20taking%20a%20big%20bite%20of%20his%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20manager%20didn't%20seem%20to%20care%20at%20all%2C%20offered%20me%20a%20refund%2C%20of%20course%2C%20but%20the%20way%20they%20acted%20was%20as%20if%20it%20happens%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20as%20per%20multiple%20news%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696863120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F7htc0ht_kfc_625x300_29_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fcould-have-broken-a-tooth-man-finds-fried-screw-in-a-bag-of-chips-at-kfc-4464961%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20coming%20home%2C%20he%20put%20a%20handful%20of%20chips%20in%20his%20mouth%20and%20felt%20something%20metal%2C%20and%20found%20a%20fried%20screw.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fcould-have-broken-a-tooth-man-finds-fried-screw-in-a-bag-of-chips-at-kfc-4464961%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fcould-have-broken-a-tooth-man-finds-fried-screw-in-a-bag-of-chips-at-kfc-4464961%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fcould-have-broken-a-tooth-man-finds-fried-screw-in-a-bag-of-chips-at-kfc-4464961%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Israeli%20Drone%20Footage%20Claims%20Attack%20On%20Hamas%20Hideouts%20In%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHigh-altitude%20footage%20released%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fisrael%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIsrael%3C%2Fa%3E%20Defense%20Forces%20-%20and%20shared%20online%20by%20an%20open-source%20intelligence%20handle%20Monday%20evening%20-%20spotlighted%20devastating%20aerial%20strikes%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fhamas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHamas%3C%2Fa%3E%20position