n%20Southern%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBrandeis%20University%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%C2%A0%20''We%20at%20Brandeis%20are%20deeply%20saddened%20to%20learn%20that%20Professor%20Troen%20has%20lost%20his%20daughter%20and%20son-in-law%20in%20the%20tragic%20events%20that%20are%20currently%20taking%20place%20in%20Israel.%20Ilan%2C%20a%20Brandeis%20alumnus%2C%20and%20his%20family%20have%20long%20been%20treasured%20members%20of%20the%20Brandeis%20community%2C%20and%20we%20hold%20Ilan%2C%20his%20wife%20Carol%2C%20and%20his%20entire%20family%20in%20our%20thoughts.%20We%20condemn%20in%20the%20strongest%20way%20terrorism%20such%20as%20we%20have%20seen%20today%20perpetrated%20against%20innocent%20civilians.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20this%20well-rehearsed%20and%20planned%20act%20of%20unbridled%20violence%20was%20not%20the%20consequence%20of%20an%20individual's%20madness%20or%20evil%20but%20the%20product%20of%20a%20government%20that%20some%20give%20public%20recognition%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Troen%20said%20of%20Hamas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%C2%A0Hamas%20militants%20launched%20a%20surprise%20assault%20on%20Israel%2C%C2%A0killing%20more%20than%20600%20Israelis%20and%20escaping%20with%20dozens%20of%20hostages.%C2%A0Israel%20responded%20with%20airstrikes%20on%20Gaza%2C%20and%20the%20conflict%20has%20since%20escalated.%C2%A0The%20Israeli%20army%20said%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20soldiers%20were%20deployed%20to%20fight%20terrorists%20in%20southern%20desert%20regions%20near%20the%20coastal%20enclave%2C%20to%20rescue%20Israeli%20hostages%20and%20then%20evacuate%20the%20entire%20region%20within%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20warned%20Gaza%20civilians%20to%20get%20away%20from%20all%20Hamas%20sites%20which%20he%20has%20vowed%20to%20turn%20%26quot%3Bto%20rubble%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Caside%20data-track-module%3D%5C%22trending-post-strip_article%5C%22%20data-vars-type%3D%5C%22trendin