Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09165836%2FScreenshot-2023-10-09-at-4.57.29%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20announced%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%209%2C%20that%20the%20four%20state%20governments%20run%20by%20the%20party%20will%20conduct%20a%20caste%20survey%20and%20follow%20it%20up%20with%20a%20socio-economic%20survey.%20Gandhi%20announced%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20(CWC)%E2%80%99s%20decision%20earlier%20this%20morning%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20four%20Congress%20chief%20ministers%20%E2%80%93%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20what%20was%20a%20clear%20display%20of%20strength%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20the%20CWC%20has%20unanimously%20decided%20to%20not%20merely%20support%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20pan-Indian%20caste%20census%20but%20also%20pressure%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20to%20conduct%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20historic%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20CWC.%20We%20will%20not%20merely%20support%20it%20but%20also%20force%20the%20BJP%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20caste%20census%20or%20get%20out%20of%20the%20way%20so%20that%20we%20can%20do%20it.%20The%20country%20needs%20a%20caste%20census%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wayanad%20MP%20said%20that%20a%20census%20that%20reveals%20the%20composition%20of%20OBC%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20communities%20in%20the%20country%20will%20open%20up%20a%20window%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20development%20paradigm%E2%80%9D.%20He%20likened%20a%20caste%20census%20to%20an%20X-ray%20which%20will%20help%20the%20governments%20diagnose%20the%20real%20problems%20and%20help%20increase%20the%20participation%20of%20the%20poor%20in%20governance.%20He%20added%20that%20while%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20attempting%20to%20deflect%20public%20attention%20from%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20assert%20its%20weight%20on%20the%20issue%20as%20a%20caste%20census%20is%20about%20identifying%20the%20poor%20of%20the%20country%20and%20knowing%20if%20they%20have%20proportionate%20%3Cem%3Ehissedari%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0or%20participation%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20government%20and%20other%20public%20institutions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20has%2010%20chief%20ministers%20but%20only%20one%20of%20them%20is%20an%20OBC.%20Even%20he%20is%20on%20his%20way%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20indirectly%20referring%20to%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20who%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fshivraj-chouhan-position-bommai-defeat-bjp-madhya-pradesh%5C%22%3Eallegedly%20being%20sidelined%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20BJP%20machinery.%20With%20the%20presence%20of%20Gehlot%2C%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20and%20Baghel%20%E2%80%93%20all%20belonging%20to%20OBC%20communities%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20dais%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20sought%20to%20make%20the%20contrast%20evident.%20Gandhi%20averred%20that%20he%20was%20confident%20of%20his%20party%20winning%20the%20upcoming%20state%20elections%20because%20of%20the%20development%20work%20done%20by%20the%20Congress%20chief%20ministers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20highlighted%20the%20policies%20of%20each%20chief%20minister%20as%20models%20that%20the%20Congress%20could%20implement%20at%20the%20central%20level%20if%20elected%20to%20power.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20public%20health%20care%20initiatives%3B%20Sukhu%E2%80%99s%20prompt%20ground-level%20disaster%20management%20during%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20floods%3B%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20prioritise%20farmers%E2%80%99%20issues%2C%20like%20giving%20them%20the%20best%20rates%20for%20their%20crops%3B%20and%20Siddaramaiah%E2%80%99s%20social%20security%20measures%20for%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20Modi%20has%20still%20not%20issued%20any%20clarification%20about%20his%20pointer%20in%20the%20Parliament%20that%20only%20three%20of%20the%2090%20bureaucrats%20working%20as%20secretaries%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20belong%20to%20OBC%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CA%20caste%20census%20is%20a%20very%20progressive%20step%20for%20the%20emancipation%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20future%20of%20our%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20CWC%E2%80%99s%20unanimous%20decision%20to%20support%20a%20caste%20census%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20decision%E2%80%9D%20or%20even%20a%20move%20about%20%E2%80%9Ccaste%20or%20religious%20politics%E2%80%9D%20but%20about%20%3Cem%3Enyay%3C%2Fem%3E%20(justice)%20for%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20caste%20census%20data%20comes%2C%20we%20will%20know%20where%20the%20%3Cem%3Edhan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(resources%20or%20money)%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWhat%20a%20sixer%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40RahulGandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20Caste%20Census%20Press%20Conference.%20He%20asked%20the%20journalists%20present%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20of%20you%20are%20Dalits%3F%20No%20one%20raised%20their%20hand!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20of%20you%20are%20Adivasis%3F%20No%20one%20raised%20their%20hand!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20of%20you%20are%20OBCs%3F%20No%20one%20raised%20their%20hand!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20then%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FrlQ34Nkl2q%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FrlQ34Nkl2q%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Srivatsa%20(%40srivatsayb)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsrivatsayb%2Fstatus%2F1711324513483313212%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%209%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20governments%2C%20too%2C%20are%20at%20fault%20for%20not%20releasing%20the%20caste%20census%20data%2C%20referring%20to%20the%202011%20Socio-Wconomic%20and%20Caste%20Census%20conducted%20by%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20what%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20earlier%2C%20we%20will%20do%20it%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CWC%20also%20passed%20a%20resolution%20that%20welcomed%20the%20Justice%20G.%20Rohini%20commission%20for%20sub-categorisation%20of%20OBCs%20but%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20back%20it%20up%20with%20%E2%80%9Cdetailed%20data%20on%20the%20socio-economic%20position%20of%20various%20communities%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20the%20Congress%20said%20could%20be%20obtained%20%E2%80%9Ceither%20from%20the%20still%20unreleased%20data%20from%20the%202011%20socio-economic%20and%20caste%20census%20or%20a%20fresh%20caste%20census.%E2%80%9D%20Recently%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20released%20its%20own%20caste%20survey%20data%20and%20will%20soon%20release%20the%20socio-economic%20indices%20of%20around%20211%20caste%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20being%20asked%20whether%20all%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20parties%20have%20the%20same%20opinion%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20them%20believe%20that%20a%20caste%20census%20should%20be%20conducted.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20might%20be%20a%20few%20who%20have%20a%20slightly%20different%20opinion%20but%20that%20is%20not%20a%20problem.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20a%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20going%20to%20support%20and%20also%20push%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20caste%20census%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAlmost%2050%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%20belongs%20to%20OBC.%20We%20believe%20that%20they%20should%20have%20a%20proportionate%20right%20to%20drive%20government%20decisions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20He%20said%20that%20while%20Modi%20may%20belong%20to%20an%20OBC%20community%2C%20he%20has%20only%20%E2%80%9Cdistracted%E2%80%9D%20the%20OBC%20communities%20from%20demanding%20proportionate%20participation%20in%20the%20government.%20%E2%80%9COur%20question%20is%20whether%20they%20are%20getting%20proportionate%20representation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20are%20elected%20to%20power%2C%20we%20will%20release%20the%20caste%20census%20data%20(conducted%20in%202011)%20on%20the%20first%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKharge%E2%80%99s%20remarks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20the%20CWC%20met%20for%20the%20second%20time%20after%20its%20marathon%20meeting%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20September%2016%2C%202023.%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20chaired%20the%20meeting%2C%20summing%20up%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20decisions%20taken%20in%20the%20last%20meeting%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6we%20collectively%20resolved%20to%20free%20the%20country%20from%20divisive%20and%20polarising%20politics%2C%20strengthen%20the%20forces%20of%20social%20equity%20and%20justice%2C%20and%20provide%20the%20people%20a%20Union%20Government%20that%20is%20responsible%2C%20responsive%2C%20sensitive%2C%20transparent%20and%20accountable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20his%20opening%20remarks.%20He%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20deliberately%20delaying%20the%20historic%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20by%20linking%20it%20to%20the%20census%20and%20the%20delimitation%20process%2C%20and%20for%20not%20keeping%20the%20opposition%20parties%20in%20the%20loop%20regarding%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20agenda%20before%20calling%20a%20special%20session%20of%20the%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20is%20still%20wondering%20why%20the%20Bill%20was%20not%20implemented%20immediately%20and%20why%20OBC%20women%20were%20excluded%20from%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20Bill.%20Why%20were%20the%20clauses%20of%20census%20and%20delimitation%20added%20to%20complicate%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%3F%20It%20is%20unclear%20when%20it%20will%20turn%20into%20reality.%20So%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20Bill%20was%20only%20brought%20for%20marketing%20and%20vote-bank%20politics%20with%20no%20intention%20of%20its%20expeditious%20implementation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20president%20also%20took%20note%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20continued%20absence%20from%20the%20conflict-ridden%20Manipur.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20prime%20minister%20who%20could%20not%20find%20time%20to%20visit%20Manipur%20even%20once%20in%20the%20last%205%20months%20to%20provide%20succour%20and%20relief%20to%20the%20much%20wounded%20sisters%20and%20brothers%20of%20Manipur%20finds%20umpteen%20opportunities%20for%20electioneering%20and%20spreading%20a%20web%20of%20lies%20and%20falsehoods%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20told%20the%20CWC%20members%20that%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20let%20people%20know%20that%20the%20first%20steps%20towards%20a%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20were%20initiated%20by%20the%20Congress%20governments%20to%20defeat%20the%20%E2%80%9Clies%E2%80%9D%20peddled%20by%20BJP%20leaders%20who%20claimed%20that%20the%20Congress%20only%20supported%20the%20Bill%20out%20of%20compulsion.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20Shri%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20vision%20that%20led%20to%20the%20Amendment%2C%20which%20aimed%20to%20provide%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20at%20the%20Panchayat%20and%20Urban%20Local%20Bodies.%20Thanks%20to%20this%2C%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20elected%20women%20in%20the%20world%20are%20in%20India%20(around%2014%20lakh)%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20reiterated%20that%20the%20party%20has%20been%20consistently%20supporting%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20census%20which%20will%20entail%20%E2%80%9Cproper%20implementation%20and%20delivery%20of%20government%20programmes%20and%20welfare%20schemes%E2%80%9D.%20He%20spoke%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commission-assembly-mizoram-madhya-pradesh-chhattisgarh-rajasthan-telangana%5C%22%3Eupcoming%20assembly%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Mizoram%20and%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20emphasised%20on%20the%20need%20for%20the%20party%20to%20replicate%20the%20%E2%80%9Csuccessful%20strategy%E2%80%9D%20of%20Karnataka%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20that%20resulted%20in%20electoral%20victories.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20light%20of%20this%2C%20considering%20that%20we%20have%20already%20solidified%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20conducted%20three%20productive%20meetings%2C%20we%20must%20expedite%20our%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20favourable%20results%20in%20the%20General%20Elections%20and%20hit%20the%20ground%20running.%20We%20need%20to%20highlight%20the%20failures%20of%20the%20government%20and%20constantly%20raise%20issues%20concerning%20the%20common%20people%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696851326000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09165836%2FScreenshot-2023-10-09-at-4.57.29%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fcongress-state-governments-caste-and-socio-economic-surveys-cwc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20took%20a%20unanimous%20decision%20to%20conduct%20the%20surveys%20as%20they%20would%20open%20up%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20development%20paradigm%E2%80%9D%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%2