.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-hamas-war-how-palestinian-militants-caught-the-middle-easts-most-powerful-army-off-guard-12981008%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-hamas-war-how-palestinian-militants-caught-the-middle-easts-most-powerful-army-off-guard-12981008%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20Govt%20Refuses%20to%20Allow%20Jailed%20Opposition%20Leader%20Khaleda%20Zia%20to%20Travel%20for%20Medical%20Treatment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F20182800%2FSecretary_Kerry_Poses_for_a_Photo_With_Government_Opposition_Leader_Begum_Khaled_Zia_at_U.S._Embassy_Dhaka_29284522026.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bangladesh%20government%20has%20refused%20to%20grant%20permission%20to%20the%20Khaleda%20Zia%2C%20the%20ailing%20opposition%20leader%20put%20under%20house%20arrest%2C%20to%20travel%20abroad%20for%20specialised%20medical%20treatment%20unavailable%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dhakatribune.com%2Fbangladesh%2F327471%2Fkhaleda-zia-requires-urgent-liver-transplant%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDhaka%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%2C%20the%20medical%20board%20formed%20by%20the%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20government%20some%20months%20ago%20at%20the%20Evercare%20Hospital%20located%20in%20the%20capital%20city%20addressed%20a%20press%20meet%20in%20Dhaka%20on%20October%209%20to%20state%20that%20Zia%20has%20been%20suffering%20from%20liver%20cirrhosis%20and%20urgently%20needs%20a%20transplant.%20Since%20a%20liver%20transplant%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20carried%20out%20in%20any%20hospital%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20she%20needs%20to%20travel%20abroad%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKhaleda%20Zia%E2%80%99s%20risk%20of%20death%20is%20high%20and%20she%20needs%20urgent%20overseas%20treatment%20for%20a%20liver%20transplant%2C%E2%80%9D%20F.M.%20Siddiqui%2C%20one%20of%20the%20doctors%20on%20the%20medical%20board%2C%20told%20reporters%20at%20the%20meet.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CKhaleda%20Zia%E2%80%99s%20liver%20infection%20has%20caused%20fluid%20to%20accumulate%20in%20her%20stomach%20repeatedly.%20High%20dosages%20of%20antibiotics%20have%20proven%20ineffective.%20Fluid%20buildup%20has%20impacted%20her%20heart%2C%20resulting%20in%20her%20being%20shifted%20to%20the%20CCU%20twice.%E2%80%9D%20The%20news%20report%20quoting%20the%20medical%20board%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20exhausted%20all%20available%20treatment%20options%20available%20domestically.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20medical%20board%20has%20been%20insisting%20on%20her%20need%20to%20travel%20aboard.%20On%20October%201%2C%20Zia%E2%80%99s%20family%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20allow%20her%20to%20travel%20aboard%20for%20better%20treatment.%20The%20same%20day%2C%20the%20law%20ministry%20denied%20permission%20citing%20legal%20provisions.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailystar.net%2Fnews%2Fbangladesh%2Fnews%2Fweve-done-all-we-can-nothing-more-do-khaledas-medical-board-3438516%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDaily%20Star%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20home%20minister%20Asaduzzaman%20Khan%20Kamal%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%20existing%20law%2C%20there%20is%20no%20scope%20for%20granting%20the%20application%20to%20let%20BNP%20Chairperson%20Khaleda%20Zia%20go%20abroad.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2078-year-old%20BNP%20chairperson%20has%20been%20suffering%20from%20multiple%20diseases%20including%20diabetes%20and%20arthritis.%20Since%20her%20conditional%20release%20from%20prison%20in%202020%20due%20to%20the%20threat%20of%20COVID-19%2C%20she%20has%20been%20living%20in%20her%20residence%20in%20Gulshan%20area%20of%20Dhaka%20and%20receiving%20treatment%20at%20the%20Evercare%20Hospital.%20In%20August%20she%20was%20hospitalised%20after%20her%20condition%20became%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%202018%2C%20Zia%20has%20been%20serving%20a%2017-year%20jail%20