increasing%20the%20seats%20for%20the%20upcoming%20session%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vishal%20Sharma%2C%20the%20media%20in-charge%20and%20a%20faculty%20member%20at%20CSJM%20University%2C%20told%20the%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20class%20is%20full%20of%20people%20who%20are%20excited%20to%20study%20the%20subject%20which%20we%20have%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20discussing%20at%20home%20and%20outside%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20the%20students%2C%20Punit%20Tiwari%2C%2039%2C%20told%20the%20newspaper.%20Tiwari%20runs%20a%20CCTV%20outsourcing%20business%20in%20Kanpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Tiwari%2C%20the%20students%20belong%20to%20various%20backgrounds%2C%20including%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20are%20retired%20government%20employees.%20He%20added%20that%20most%20of%20the%20students%20have%20enrolled%20in%20the%20course%20out%20of%20personal%20interest%20in%20the%20subject%2C%20and%20not%20for%20job%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20refused%20to%20verify%20or%20deny%20these%20claims%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20courses%20were%20launched%20under%20the%20New%20Education%20Policy%202020%2C%20aiming%20to%20promote%20%E2%80%9Cancient%20and%20eternal%20Indian%20knowledge%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20daily%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20courses%20are%20structured%20around%20a%20flexible%20credit%20system%20and%20have%20been%20developed%20with%20the%20input%20of%20scholars%20in%20Sanskrit%20education.%20The%20curriculum%20for%20the%20certificate%20course%20includes%20subjects%20like%20methods%20of%20worship%20and%20an%20introduction%20to%20the%20almanac%2C%20while%20the%20master%E2%80%99s%20programme%20in%20Jyotirvigyan%20focuses%20on%20modern%20and%20scientific%20aspects%20of%20ancient%20Vedic%20astronomical%20and%20astrological%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilar%20Karmkand%20courses%20have%20been%20introduced%20at%20Gorakhpur%20and%20Lucknow%20University%2C%20and%20more%20universi