dia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-1696597357-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331726%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAsha%20dedicates%20post-school%20hours%20and%20holidays%20to%20training%20sessions.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20vigour%20comes%20from%20within%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F57380%2Fsimple-self-defense-techniques-everyone-needs-to-know%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportance%20of%20self-defence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Asha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSelf-defence%20is%2090%20percent%20mental%20and%20only%2010%20percent%20physical.%20It%20is%20just%20about%20your%20determination%20that%20comes%20from%20within.%20Girls%20believe%20that%20they%20are%20weak%20physically%20so%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20fight%20men.%20But%20if%20you%20are%20trained%20enough%2C%20you%20can%20protect%20yourself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsha%20dedicates%20post-school%20hours%20and%20holidays%20to%20training%20sessions%20where%20each%20session%20is%20split%20into%20six%20days.%20Explaining%20her%20strategy%20to%20train%20girls%20with%20disabilities%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTraining%20them%20is%20a%20little%20different%20as%20they%20can%20only%20sense%20someone%20by%20touch%20while%20abled%20persons%20can%20perceive%20danger%20by%20seeing%20the%20perpetrator%20or%20even%20hearing%20their%20conversations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20girls%20with%20disabilities%2C%20I%20utilise%20daily%20work%20experiences%20like%20brushing%20teeth%20or%20kicking%20a%20football%20into%20attack%20positions.%20By%20using%20a%20dummy%2C%20we%20tell%20them%20if%20they%20sense%20danger%20from%20behind%20them%2C%20they%20then%20could%20hit%20them%20by%20bending%20their%20elbow%20in%20a%20similar%20manner%20when%20they%20brush%20their%20teeth.%20Or%20they%20could%20kick%20them%20like%20they%20would%20kick%20a%20football.%20When%20they%20hit%20the%20dummy%20themselves%2C%20they%20build%20confidence.%20With%20training%2C%20they%20learn%20how%20they%20could%20convert%20their%20body%20into%20a%20weapon%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20I%20tell%20my%20students%20to%20try%20negotiations%20first.%20%3Cem%3EPar%20agar%20baaton%20se%20kaam%20na%20chale%2C%20to%20laaton%20se%20kaam%20chalao.%20Aur%20laton%20pe%20aa%20jaaye%20to%20jhukna%20nahi%20hai.%20%3C%2Fem%3E(But%20when%20negotiations%20fail%20to%20work%2C%20hit%20them%20hard%2C%20and%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20that%2C%20then%20there%20should%20be%20no%20backing%20down)%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecalling%20one%20such%20incident%2C%20Asha%20explains%20how%20she%20once%20saw%20a%20girl%20dragging%20a%20%3Cem%3Echhora%3C%2Fem%3E%20(boy)%20by%20his%20shirt%E2%80%99s%20collar%20and%20bringing%20him%20to%20her.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20told%20me%20how%20he%20passed%20comments%20on%20her.%20The%20guy%20apologised%20to%20us%20and%20even%20pledged%20not%20to%20flirt%20with%20any%20woman%20ever%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Asha%20was%20awarded%20the%20National%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Award%202023%20by%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-2-1696597371-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%