2C%20is%20paramount%20for%20Asha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20this%20work%20because%20it%20gives%20me%20personal%20happiness.%20Now%2C%20I%20sleep%20peacefully%20knowing%20the%20girls%20I%20trained%20will%20be%20able%20to%20protect%20themselves%20from%20the%20humiliation%20that%20was%20once%20caused%20to%20one%20of%20my%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fnationalcrimerecordsbureau%2Fpost%2F1679310394CII2021Volume1.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECrime%20In%20India%202021%20Volume%20I%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3EBy%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs)%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Asha%20Suman%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696603084000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-1-1696597320.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alwar's%20Asha%20Suman%20has%20dedicated%20her%20life%20to%20imparting%20self-defence%20skills%20to%20young%20girls.%20So%20far%2C%20she%20has%20trained%2030%2C000%20girls%20across%20Rajasthan.%20This%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Day%2C%20she%20was%20conferred%20with%20the%20National%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Award%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331721%2Frajasthan-government-school-teacher-trains-self-defense-to-girls-with-disabilities-national-award%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22These%20Pilots%20Were%20Sued%20For%20Quitting.%20They%20Say%20It%20Was%20Dangerous%20To%20Stay.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22A%20small%20airline%20has%20taken%20roughly%2080%20former%20pilots%20to%20court%20over%20training%20debts.%20In%20interviews%2C%20many%20cited%20safety%20concern