iends%20made%20me%20realise%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20more%20talk%20on%20mental%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajesh%2C%20a%20Mumbai%20resident%2C%20vouches%20for%20the%20role%20that%20therapy%20plays%20in%20improving%20mental%20health.%20%E2%80%9CI%20lost%20my%20job%20and%20my%20father%20during%20COVID.%20I%20was%20in%20the%20lowest%20phase%20of%20my%20life%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20who%20to%20turn%20to%20for%20help.%20I%20just%20stayed%20home%20for%20almost%2045%20days%20without%20even%20stepping%20foot%20outside.%20When%20speaking%20to%20my%20children%2C%20friends%20and%20family%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20my%20wife%20urged%20me%20to%20try%20therapy.%20I%20scoffed%2C%20but%20she%20insisted%20I%20take%20an%20online%20session.%20It%20really%20helped.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20realise%20many%20more%20things%20about%20myself%20and%20I%20am%20able%20to%20deal%20with%20my%20failures%20better.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPooja%20felt%20that%20there%20was%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20stigma%20around%20mental%20health.%20To%20bridge%20that%20gap%2C%20in%202019%2C%20she%20started%20an%20NGO%20called%20Transfomind%20Foundation%20%E2%80%94%20an%20online%20platform%20to%20create%20awareness%20of%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20collaborated%20with%20mental%20health%20experts%20to%20develop%20educational%20material%20on%20mental%20well-being.%20This%20idea%20gained%20traction%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20raising%20significant%20awareness.%20In%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20teamed%20up%20with%20Montfort%20College%20to%20offer%20free%20therapy%20sessions%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20also%20a%20challenging%20time%20in%20Pooja%E2%80%99s%20personal%20life%20as%20she%20was%20separated%20from%20her%20husband.%20During%20a%20solo%20trip%2C%20a%20conversation%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20mental%20health%20ignited%20the%20fire%20in%20