ime%20was%20used%20for%20plastering%2C%20masonry%2C%20and%20the%20roof.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20green%20oasis%20in%20Rajasthan%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20construction%2C%20the%20couple%20made%20sure%20to%20have%20good%20ventilation%20and%20lighting.%20They%20installed%20windows%20in%20the%20West%20direction%20to%20let%20in%20ample%20light.%20Because%20the%20South%20direction%20gets%20the%20most%20sunlight%2C%20the%20couple%20positioned%20their%20bedrooms%20in%20the%20North-East%20and%20South-East%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRajasthan%20remains%20hot%20throughout%20the%20year%20except%20December%20and%20January.%20So%2C%20avoiding%20heat%20was%20our%20primary%20concern.%20The%20temperature%20inside%20our%20room%20remains%205%20to%207%20degrees%20cooler%20than%20the%20outside.%20We%20do%20not%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F262389%2Fbengaluru-sustainable-mud-home-how-to-build-ecofriendly-save-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair%20conditioners%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20all.%20Meanwhile%2C%20in%20winter%2C%20we%20bask%20in%20the%20sunlight%20in%20our%20South%20and%20South-East%20facing%20balcony%20and%20verandah%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ashis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20planted%20many%20trees%20in%20the%20area%20to%20regulate%20the%20house%E2%80%99s%20temperature.%20They%20also%20cultivate%20over%20200%20varieties%20of%20seasonal%20vegetables%20and%20fruits%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20bottle%20gourd%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20bitter%20gourd%2C%20lemons%2C%20grapes%2C%20bananas%2C%20and%20pomegranates.%20These%20provide%2080%20percent%20of%20their%20vegetable%20and%20fruit%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%